{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So they left us alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So, he actually was trying, and to a certain degree, saved our lives, as long as he could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the work itself, even though it was physical, it was-- I was young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was then 15 and 16.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And, of course, Saturdays we had free, and Sunday so we would-- even in the ghetto, we would eke out some kind of a social life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know, kids always find a way of surviving somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I always wanted to meet with the girls, with the boys and strike up a friendship with [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Yahzhah. ?] And we would meet in someone's apartment-- apartment, I mean, this one room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They would go out for the afternoon and let us kids in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And one of them had the old record player, gramophone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We would wind it up and put this record on there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I used to love to listen to on the console radio.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was the same type music I used to listen to from BBC.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was like Benny Goodman and Glenn Miller, Tex Beneke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it was a different type of music.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we would try to make up some steps and try to learn how to dance to what we thought was a strange, crazy kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And this is how we'd spend our social part of the ghetto life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And then I was asked to play a harmonica or sing a song.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we would dance a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And those were are the pleasant memories of kids and the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yahzhah ?] and I became friends, close friends then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not real close, not sanctioned by their parents, god forbid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they would be mad if-- what do mean, you're 16.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
